{"tid":816873,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"To 求緊山竹打黎香港既on9","createTime":"2018-09-13T04:24:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T02:27:57.000Z","uid":137406,"like":87,"dislike":296,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"0ef17f0277ad834e7906ee9e3566c6a3f91b727d","tid":816873,"uid":137406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T04:24:41.000Z","msg":"你地可能以為好少事<br />\n最多咪8號10號風球<br />\n眼見咁多on9求打風真係好心痛<br />\n點解香港人依家反智成咁?? 為左放假竟然望天災發生<br />\n而家講緊嘅係可能係近10年最強嘅颱風<br />\n比上星期打日本個飛燕勁好L多<br />\n你唔信睇下成個台風既size，就快大過成個日本<br />\n有冇諗過農作物會失收, 建築物頂唔頂得順, 幾多動物會死? 影響幾多人生計?<br />\n係咪真係要有人死先安樂? 有冇諗過出事個個係你家人你會點?<br />\n香港係無任何防災準備, 危機意識又低<br />\n<br />\n我好希望今次力場可以幫我地擋風, 一齊集氣趕走山竹。"},{"pid":"a3ba90453c0e675853bd9b48e237832c2702a1dd","tid":816873,"uid":137406,"like":3,"dislike":55,"score":-52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T04:25:30.000Z","msg":"趕走風災由波台開始<br />\n<br />\n希望各位CHING可以十卜"},{"pid":"a1fe87e634bd5c9e105083dd842d15211bd3709c","tid":816873,"uid":124667,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"a3ba90453c0e675853bd9b48e237832c2702a1dd","tid":816873,"uid":137406,"like":3,"dislike":55,"score":-52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T04:25:30.000Z","msg":"趕走風災由波台開始<br />\n<br />\n希望各位CHING可以十卜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T04:26:02.000Z","msg":"十卜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcdfd546634ce5e1ca71c7bbc513e7387afb6ef9","tid":816873,"uid":87155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T04:26:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"324b6dad495cec136ac718aa46787c1afbf8252e","tid":816873,"uid":137406,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"a1fe87e634bd5c9e105083dd842d15211bd3709c","tid":816873,"uid":124667,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"a3ba90453c0e675853bd9b48e237832c2702a1dd","tid":816873,"uid":137406,"like":3,"dislike":55,"score":-52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T04:25:30.000Z","msg":"趕走風災由波台開始<br />\n<br />