（即10號風球），因此具有很強的荷載抵禦能力，在這種情形下，發生烈度5至6級地震時，99%以上的建築仍然安全，即使發生烈度為7級，約475年一遇的地震，本港96%的建築物仍然安全，而多項主要基建設施（例如機場、道路橋樑、鐵路橋樑、水塘及污水隧道），設計上都能抵禦烈度6至8級的地震。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%BB%BA%E7%AF%89%E8%80%90%E9%A2%B1%E9%A2%A8%20%20%E5%B9%BE%E5%90%8C%E6%8A%97%E9%9C%87/web_tc/article/20150308/s00285/1425752091423\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E7%25AF%2589%25E8%2580%2590%25E9%25A2%25B1%25E9%25A2%25A8%2520%2520%25E5%25B9%25BE%25E5%2590%258C%25E6%258A%2597%25E9%259C%2587%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20150308%2Fs00285%2F1425752091423&d=uWKPkhDhjQm3ykyRRWunqLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=197ec78e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E7%25AF%2589%25E8%2580%2590%25E9%25A2%25B1%25E9%25A2%25A8%2520%2520%25E5%25B9%25BE%25E5%2590%258C%25E6%258A%2597%25E9%259C%2587%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20150308%2Fs00285%2F1425752091423&h=35f9c7bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%BB%BA%E7%AF%89%E8%80%90%E9%A2%B1%E9%A2%A8%20%20%E5%B9%BE%E5%90%8C%E6%8A%97%E9%9C%87/web_tc/article/20150308/s00285/1425752091423</a>"},{"pid":"e1f092e2b94bfdbf7eb94f7f2a4e368fc080d3f1","tid":816873,"uid":151664,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T04:49:08.000Z","msg":"香港唔受吓災難，只會愈嚟愈離地。<br />\n最好風災雨災股災、沙士一齊嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73e17e0b6df61922c58e20b37e1bf1f6f3691cde","tid":816873,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"72d1245962592244fc65cc39c98c6e86513344e8","tid":816873,"uid":124667,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"324b6dad495cec136ac718aa46787c1afbf8252e","tid":816873,"uid":137406,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"a1fe87e634bd5c9e105083dd842d15211bd3709c","tid":816873,"uid":124667,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13